---
import catalog from '../../../benchmarks/catalog.json';
export function getStaticPaths() {
  return catalog.components.map(component=>({params:{id:component.id},props:{component}}));
}
const {component}=Astro.props;
const frameworks=['react','vue','svelte','solid'];
---
<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"><title>{component.name} · Kumo</title><style>body{margin:0;background:#f3f4f6;color:#111827;font:16px system-ui}.topbar{padding:18px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #d1d5db;background:white}.topbar a{color:#111827;text-decoration:none;font-weight:800}.shell{max-width:1100px;margin:auto;padding:32px}h1{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:36px}p{margin:0 0 24px;color:#64748b}.tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:12px}.tab{border:1px solid #d1d5db;background:white;border-radius:999px;padding:8px 14px;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer}.tab[aria-selected="true"]{background:#111827;color:white}.frame{width:100%;height:1200px;border:1px solid #d1d5db;border-radius:12px;background:white}</style></head><body><nav class="topbar"><a href="/">← Kumo catalog</a></nav><main class="shell"><h1>{component.name} runtime comparison</h1><p>React is the canonical input; these React, Vue, Svelte, and Solid panels are proof surfaces for observable output parity. See the catalog for evidence gates, measurements, and migration limitations.</p><div class="tabs" role="tablist">{frameworks.map((framework,index)=><button class="tab" role="tab" aria-selected={index===0 ? 'true':'false'} data-framework={framework}>{framework}</button>)}</div><iframe class="frame" id="runtime-frame" src={`http://127.0.0.1:4301/${component.id}/react`} title={`${component.name} runtime`}></iframe></main><script define:vars={{componentId:component.id}}>for(const button of document.querySelectorAll('[data-framework]'))button.addEventListener('click',()=>{document.querySelectorAll('[data-framework]').forEach(item=>item.setAttribute('aria-selected',String(item===button)));document.querySelector('#runtime-frame').src=`http://127.0.0.1:4301/${componentId}/${button.dataset.framework}`})</script></body></html>
